      "content": "hey, quick question... im on sertraline for my depression but it feels like it's not really doing enough lately and i'm super stressed with uni exams coming up. i was thinking about adding some st johns wort to my routine to help boost my mood a bit, since it's natural. is it okay to take them together?",
