    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh wow okay, i didnt realize it was that serious. i thought since it was just an herbal supplement it wouldn't be a big deal. are you sure though? i've heard from some people that if you just take a small dose of the herbal stuff it's fine and won't interfere with the meds too much.",
